quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Dájúdájú A ti fún (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm ní ìmọ̀nà tirẹ̀ ṣíwájú (kí ó tó dàgbà). Àwa sì ń jẹ́ Onímọ̀ nípa rẹ̀
  21,52,"(Rántí) nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti ìjọ rẹ̀ pé: “Kí ni àwọn ère wọ̀nyí tí ẹ̀ ń dúró tì lọ́rùn ṣe jẹ́ ná?”"
  21,53,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A bá àwọn bàbá wa tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún wọn ni.”"
  21,54,"Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin àti àwọn bàbá yín ti wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”"
  21,55,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣé o mú òdodo wá fún wa ni tàbí ìwọ wà lára àwọn ẹlẹ́fẹ̀.”"
  21,56,"Ó sọ pé: \"Rárá. Olúwa yin ni Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀; Ẹni tí Ó pílẹ̀ ìṣẹ̀dá wọn. Èmi sì wà nínú àwọn ẹlẹ́rìí lórí ìyẹn"
  21,57,"Àti pé mo fi Allāhu búra, dájúdájú mo máa dète sí àwọn òrìṣà yín lẹ́yìn tí ẹ bá pẹ̀yìn dà, tí ẹ lọ"
  21,58,Ó sì fọ́ wọn sí wẹ́wẹ́ àfi àgbà (òrìṣà) wọn nítorí kí wọ́n lè padà dé bá a
  21,59,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ta ni ó ṣe èyí pẹ̀lú àwọn ọlọ́hun wa? Dájúdájú onítọ̀un wà nínú àwọn alábòsí.”"
  21,60,"Wọ́n wí pé: “A gbọ́ tí ọ̀dọ́kùnrin kan ń bu ẹnu àtẹ́ lù wọ́n. Wọ́n ń pe (ọmọ náà) ní ’Ibrọ̄hīm.”"
  21,61,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ẹ mú un wá han àwọn ènìyàn kí wọ́n lè jẹ́rìí lé e lórí.”"
  21,62,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ṣé ìwọ l’o ṣe èyí pẹ̀lú àwọn ọlọ́hun wa, ’Ibrọ̄hīm?”"
  21,63,"Ó sọ pé: “Rárá o, àgbà wọn yìí l’ó ṣe (wọ́n bẹ́ẹ̀). Nítorí náà, ẹ bi wọ́n léèrè wò tí wọ́n bá máa ń sọ̀rọ̀.”"
  21,64,"Nígbà náà, wọ́n yíjú síra wọn, wọ́n sì wí pé: “Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin ni alábòsí.”"
  21,65,"Lẹ́yìn náà, wọ́n sorí kọ́ (wọ́n sì wí pé): “Ìwọ náà kúkú mọ̀ pé àwọn wọ̀nyí kì í sọ̀rọ̀.”"
  21,66,"Ó sọ pé: \"Ṣé ẹ̀yin yóò máa jọ́sìn fún n̄ǹkan tí kò lè ṣe yín ní àǹfààní, tí kò sì lè kó ìnira ba yín lẹ́yìn Allāhu"
  21,67,"Ṣíọ̀ ẹ̀yin àti n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún lẹ́yìn Allāhu, ṣé ẹ̀yin kò níí ṣe làákàyè ni"
  21,68,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ẹ dáná sun ún; kí ẹ sì ran àwọn ọlọ́hun yín lọ́wọ́, tí ẹ̀yin bá níkan-án ṣe.”"
  21,69,"A sọ pé: “Iná, di tútù àti àlàáfíà lára ’Ibrọ̄hīm.”"
  21,70,"Wọ́n gbèrò ète sí i, ṣùgbọ́n A ṣe wọ́n ní olófò jùlọ"
  21,71,A sì gba òun àti Lūt là sórí ilẹ̀ tí A fi ìbùkún sí fún gbogbo ẹ̀dá
  21,72,"A ta á ní ọrẹ ọmọ, ’Is-hāƙ àti Ya‘ƙūb tí ó jẹ́ àlékún (ìyẹn, ọmọọmọ). Olúkùlùkù (wọn) ni A ṣe ní ẹni rere"
  21,73,"A ṣe wọ́n ní aṣíwájú t’ó ń tọ́ àwọn ènìyàn sí ọ̀nà pẹ̀lú àṣẹ Wa. A sì fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí wọn nípa ṣíṣe iṣẹ́ rere, ìrun kíkí àti Zakāh yíyọ. Wọ́n sì jẹ́ olùjọ́sìn fún Wa"
  21,74,"(Ẹ rántí Ànábì) Lūt. A fún un ní ipò Ànábì àti ìmọ̀. A sì gbà á là nínú ìlú tí wọ́n ti ń ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ burúkú. Dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ìjọ burúkú, òbìlẹ̀jẹ́"
  21,75,A sì mú un wọ inú ìkẹ́ Wa. Dájúdájú ó wà nínú àwọn ẹni rere